window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>A monster murdered. </i></p> <p>It's only 10 days since Douglas Remfry's release from prison, having served seven years for rape, and now he's dead: naked on a bare mattress in a grubby north London hotel room, his head hooded and his hands tied with a brown leather belt.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p><i>A deadly justice.</i></p> <p>Someone knew he was coming out. Someone wanted to mete out some punishment of his own.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p><i>A case no one wants solved. </i></p> <p>And when a second sex offender is found dead, DI Tom Thorne knows he has a vicious, calculating vigilante on his hands.</p>"; 
